trans-unit.source: Defines the binding element used to create a custom peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: Definerer bindingselementet brukes til å opprette et egendefinert node-Løsningsprogram.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new default instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny standardforekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class by cloning the provided custom peer resolver binding.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> klasse ved kloning av angitte egendefinerte node løseren binding.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> instance which contains the settings to clone for the new binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref>forekomsten som inneholder innstillinger for å klone for den nye bindingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class with the provided resolver settings.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> klassen med de angitte artikkelløseren-innstillingene.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref> object that contains the specific settings for the new binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref>objektet som inneholder de bestemte innstillingene for den nye bindingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class with the provided binding context and resolver settings.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> klassen med de angitte bindingen konteksten og Løsningsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext> object that contains the binding context for resolvers created by this binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>objektet som inneholder bindingen konteksten for omgjørere som er opprettet med denne bindingen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref> object that contains the specific settings for the new binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref>objektet som inneholder de bestemte innstillingene for den nye bindingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the endpoint address of the peer on which resolvers created by this binding will run.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir Endepunktsadressen av motparten som omgjørere som er opprettet med denne bindingen skal kjøres.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> object that contains the network address of the peer on which resolvers created by this binding will run.

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the network binding used by resolvers created with this binding element.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir nettverksbindingen som brukes av omgjørere som er opprettet med denne Bindingselement.
